data.description: Spacious home loaded with recent updates and upgrades! Dramatic 2-story foyer welcomes you to a spacious circular floor plan. Formal dining room with upgraded fixture leads to Gourmet kitchen. GE upgraded Appliances. Quartz tops,upgrade cabs/island! Breakfast bar overlooks huge family room/living room. Gas fp completes this area for entertaining and holidays! Downstairs has newer plank look ceramic tile floors for the most updated style! Kit has full pantry as well as walk-in laundry room that also has door to the backyard. Half bath for guests. Second entrance to Backyard from the fam room,patio,playset,fully fenced w/sprinklers and mature trees at rear fence line for added privacy. Follow the winding stairs up to your owner's retreat, complete with two separate sinks & closets, jetted tub. 3 more BRs incl. FROG, hall bath. Balcony overlooking foyer. 50 yr warranty roof & HVAC less than 10 y.o.! 2 car gar w/cabinets/bench and loft for projects/storage & 4 driveway spaces. Quick close!
